== 评价 ==
=== 专业评价 ===
影片在[[汇总媒体|汇总媒体]][[烂番茄|烂番茄]]收获319条评论，得到98%的新鲜度，平均得分8.3/10。网站共识写道：“《迈阿密的一夜》深入反思了历史伟人的经历，令人印象深刻，体现出蕾吉娜·金对个人的导演处女作拿捏得当<ref>{{Cite web |title=One Night In Miami (2020) |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/one_night_in_miami |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228020125/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/one_night_in_miami |archive-date=2020-12-28 |access-date=2021-03-19 |website=Rotten Tomatoes }}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]收录评论51条，平均得分83/100，表示“普遍好评”<ref>{{Cite web |title=One Night In Miami Reviews |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/one-night-in-miami |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110052134/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/one-night-in-miami |archive-date=2021-01-10 |access-date=2021-01-29 |website=Metacritic }}</ref>。

[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]的凯特·厄布兰（Kate Erbland）给予影片“A–”评价，认为影片经常有原版舞台剧的影子，但导演金和演员跳出舞台剧的大部分限制，频繁使用精心组装的头顶镜头，优雅地使用镜子，让众多角色实现同框<ref>{{Cite news |last=Erbland |first=Kate |date=2020-09-08 |title='One Night in Miami' Review: Regina King's Directorial Debut Is a Vibrant, Reflective Slice of History |work=IndieWire |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/09/one-night-in-miami-review-regina-king-1234584340/ |dead-url=no |access-date=2020-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200908152235/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/09/one-night-in-miami-review-regina-king-1234584340/ |archive-date=2020-09-08 }}</ref>。《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的{{tsl|en|Owen Gleiberman|欧文·格里伯曼}}赞扬角色及电影的现实意义：“《迈阿密的一夜》是一场引人入胜的随意辩论，讨论了赢得权利的人该如何使用它<ref>{{Cite web |last=Gleiberman |first=Owen |date=2020-09-07 |title='One Night in Miami' Review: A Quartet of African-American Legends Talk the Night Away in Regina King's Captivating Directorial Debut |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/reviews/one-night-in-miami-review-regina-king-1234761095/ |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907212558/https://variety.com/2020/film/reviews/one-night-in-miami-review-regina-king-1234761095/ |archive-date=2020-09-07 |access-date=2020-09-08 |website=Variety }}</ref>。”

